snippet.title: Evil Vents - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
A short survival game made in two days!
It is lurking! Evil Vents is a survival game where you are trapped inside a vent system with a creature that consumes flesh! you must find your way out or you will not be the last to be consumed!

Store: cyber752.itch.io/evil-vents

Track: “Phobia”
Music by Elysium Audio Labs
www.elysiumaudiolabs.com
bit.ly/2QmAxRW 
https://youtu.be/a5N99v5VmPk
Spotify: spoti.fi/3as7DLr
